00:03:30,793 --> 00:03:33,004
Kod Jenayah Akta 347.

57
00:03:35,048 --> 00:03:37,550
Saya tak berniat nak tipu mereka…

58
00:03:37,634 --> 00:03:39,761
Awak buat tak tahu semasa dia ditipu

59
00:03:39,844 --> 00:03:41,387
