81
00:04:32,313 --> 00:04:33,439
Tapi…

82
00:04:34,607 --> 00:04:36,317
Dia yang kata nak bayar dulu.

83
00:04:36,401 --> 00:04:38,486
Saya patut buat dia bayar dua kali ganda.

84
