00:06:48,199 --> 00:06:49,659
Perubahan sikapnya…

112
00:06:51,619 --> 00:06:52,578
Hei, Kim.

113
00:06:54,122 --> 00:06:55,540
Penangguhan perbicaraan?

114
00:06:55,623 --> 00:06:58,417
Dia akan mengaku salah jika
pemeriksaan lapangan dijalankan.

115
00:06:58,501 --> 00:07:00,586
Bekas pendakwa raya bunuh ketuanya.

116
00:07:00,670 --> 00:07:02,588
Buat malu pendakwa raya saja.

117
00:07:02,672 --> 00:07:04,173
Taklimat rasmi? Mustahil.

118
00:07:08,136 --> 00:07:09,679
Saya bukannya nak beritahu Choi.

119
00:07:09,762 --> 00:07:11,973
Ia cuma sembang kosong semasa makan.

120
00:07:12,056 --> 00:07:13,975
Kalau awak tak percaya, mari berjumpa.

121
