155
00:09:03,709 --> 00:09:05,002
Dia enggan beri keterangan.

156
00:09:06,379 --> 00:09:08,089
Kini dia nak bercakap.

157
00:09:11,634 --> 00:09:13,219
Andaikan hanya ada gula…

158
00:09:13,803 --> 00:09:15,137
Maafkan saya.

159
00:09:17,682 --> 00:09:18,683
