160
00:09:19,225 --> 00:09:21,227
Kolagen boleh makan, untuk kulit.

161
00:09:23,020 --> 00:09:23,896
Baik.

162
00:09:57,763 --> 00:09:59,849
Dia pengsan kerana hipoglisemia,

163
00:09:59,932 --> 00:10:01,642
